Williams &amp; Wilkins. p.&#160;171. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/978-0-397-51519-6\" title=\"Special:BookSources/978-0-397-51519-6\">978-0-397-51519-6</a><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">4 June</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Color+Atlas+of+Foot+and+Ankle+Dermatology&amp;rft.pages=171&amp;rft.pub=Lippincott+Williams+%26+Wilkins&amp;rft.date=1999&amp;rft.isbn=978-0-397-51519-6&amp;rft.aulast=Dockery&amp;rft.aufirst=Gary+L.&amp;rft.au=Crawford%2C+Mary+Elizabeth&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.com%2Fbooks%3Fid%3DwQkML9WQfXsC%26pg%3DPA171&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AAstringent\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-1907Dorland-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-1907Dorland_7-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\"><a href=\"/wiki/Dorland%27s_medical_reference_works\" title=\"Dorland&#39;s medical reference works\">Dorland, W. A. Newman</a> (1907). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://books.google.com/books?id=6DG6AAAAIAAJ\"><i>The american illustrated medical dictionary</i></a> (4th ed.). Philadelphia and London: W.B. Saunders company. pp.&#160;14, 39, 635<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">4 June</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=The+american+illustrated+medical+dictionary&amp;rft.place=Philadelphia+and+London&amp;rft.pages=14%2C+39%2C+635&amp;rft.edition=4th&amp;rft.pub=W.B.+Saunders+company&amp;rft.date=1907&amp;rft.aulast=Dorland&amp;rft.aufirst=W.+A.+Newman&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2